tgui-skin-desc:
Provides 2 TGUI skins:
* 2011 - The Modern version of MonoBook with fresh look and many usability improvements.
* 2022 - The TGUI built as part of the WMF [[mw:Desktop Improvements]] project.
prefs-tgui-enable-tgui-1-help: Over the next few years, we will be gradually updating the TGUI skin. Legacy TGUI will allow you to view the old version of TGUI (as of December 2019). To learn more about the updates, go to our [[mw:Reading/Web/Desktop_Improvements|project page]].
tgui.css: /* All CSS here will be loaded for users of the TGUI skin */
tgui.js: /* All JavaScript here will be loaded for users of the TGUI skin */
tgui-language-button-aria-label: Go to an article in another language. Available in {{PLURAL:$1|$1 language|$1 languages}}
tgui-no-language-button-aria-label: This article exist only in this language. Add the article for other languages
tgui-language-redirect-to-top: On this {{SITENAME}} the language links are at the top of the page across from the article title. [[#p-lang-btn|Go to top]].
